  <header>Freestyle Polo in Gilgit Baltistan</header><main>
    <h1>Freestyle Polo in Gilgit-Baltistan</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the home of one of the world's most exciting and historical sports! Polo in Gilgit-Baltistan is played in a unique, fast-paced, and rugged style, earning it the title of "Freestyle Polo" or the "Game of Kings."</p>
    <h2>History and Tradition</h2>
    <p>This version of polo has been played in the mountain valleys for centuries. Unlike the modern, regulated game, Freestyle Polo has fewer rules, larger teams, and a passionate, high-energy atmosphere.</p>
    <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polo_in_Gilgit-Baltistan" target="_blank">Read more about the history on Wikipedia</a>
</main>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Teams</h2>
    <div id="teamList"></div>

    <div class="add-box">
      <h3>Add a New Team</h3>
      <input type="text" id="teamName" placeholder="Team Name" />
      <textarea id="teamDetails" rows="3" placeholder="Team Details"></textarea>
      <button onclick="addTeam()">Add Team</button>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:30px; font-size:14px; text-align:center;">Website created by <strong>Muhammad Aba Saleh</strong></p>
  </div>

  <script>
    function loadTeams() {
      let teams = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("teams")) || [];
      let list = document.getElementById("teamList");
      list.innerHTML = "";
      teams.forEach((t, i) => {
        list.innerHTML += `
          <div class="team">
            <h3>${t.name}</h3>
            <p>${t.details}</p>
          </div>`;
      });
    }

    function addTeam() {
      let name = document.getElementById("teamName").value.trim();
      let details = document.getElementById("teamDetails").value.trim();
      if(!name || !details){ alert("Please fill both fields"); return; }

      let teams = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("teams")) || [];
      teams.push({name, details});
      localStorage.setItem("teams", JSON.stringify(teams));

      document.getElementById("teamName").value = "";
      document.getElementById("teamDetails").value = "";
      loadTeams();
    }

    loadTeams();
  </script>
 </body>
